WHO   — Miquella the Unalloyed — the Empyrean cursed with eternal youth
WHAT  — Marika's son and Malenia's twin, an Empyrean eligible for godhood, cursed with eternal childhood
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the Haligtree and unalloyed gold  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
